微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">联系人及联系方式</span></td><td width=\"68\" height=\"57\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" x:str=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">项&nbsp;&nbsp;目<br/>所在地</span></td><td width=\"61\" height=\"57\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" x:str=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">项目<br/>类别</span></td><td width=\"72\" height=\"57\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" x:str=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">牵头落<br/>实领导</span></td><td width=\"78\" height=\"57\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" x:str=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">牵头落实<br/>领导联系电话</span></td></tr><tr height=\"75\"><td width=\"40\" height=\"75\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" 00000000000000=\"\" x:num=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">1</span></td><td width=\"175\" height=\"75\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: middle; white-space: normal;\" x:str=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;\">文化创意产业园（集团新总部基地）招商项目</span></td><td width=\"183\" height=\"7